    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hi folks. In these cases, you should use a [BigInt](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/BigInt) value instead of a number. That is, instead of `10000000000000000000`, you should use `10000000000000000000n` (notice the trailing `n`).\r\n\r\nThat being said, we should show a better error in these scenarios. I'm going to open a new issue for that, and close this one in favor of it.",
